ce in Texas yesterday.\r\rPolice say the main suspect for a mass shooting in Houston on Sunday was a man armed with an AR-15 rifle and a pistol. \r\rAuthorities say they have not determined the role of a second armed man who was at the scene.\r\rReports say a gunman began shooting at an auto shop at around 10:15 a.m. A customer, believed to be in his 50s, was shot and killed at the store.\r\rThe suspect then shot at a responding officer’s squad car.\r\rHouston police posted a photo on Facebook showing the squad car riddled with 21 bullet holes. The officer inside the vehicle was not hurt.\r\rThe gunman also shot at a police helicopter that responded to the scene, hitting it at least five times.\r\rInvestigators say a fire that broke out at a nearby gas station was likely caused by gunfire hitting a gas pump.\r\rAccording to police, a total of eight people were shot, including the suspect, who was killed.\r\r原文影片請看此\rhttp://bit.ly/1Y0nHXt本新聞文字、照片、影片專供蘋果「升級壹會員」閱覽，版權所有，禁止任何媒體、社群網站、論壇，在紙本或網路部分引用、改寫、轉貼分享，違者必究。有報導指，前力霸集團總裁王又曾為參加孫女婚禮，於27日命喪車禍。不過據《蘋果》追查，洛杉磯上週末確實有位同名同姓的Wendy Wang結婚，但是新娘並非王辭茵，而是另有其人。這位新娘在知名翻譯社工作，上週六（28日）下嫁同事，婚禮在洛杉磯近郊Malibu舉行。王又曾孫女Wendy，即王令麟二女兒王辭茵，早在2012年就已經結婚。去年5月9日，王令麟長女王辭涵（Marina）在聖塔莫尼卡高級海灘酒店舉辦婚禮，王辭茵擔任「Matron of Honor」，意即已婚首席伴娘。她自己2012年的臉書照片也戴著婚戒。（呂明芬╱綜合報導）佳士得拍賣公司周一於香港舉行拍賣會，其中一只愛馬仕（ Herm&egrave;s）鑲鑽鱷魚皮包拍出逾30萬美元（約979萬元台幣）高價，締造史上最貴皮包記錄。這只有10年歷史的柏金包（Birkin）質料是罕見的白色喜瑪拉雅尼羅鱷魚皮、配上18K白金與鑲有245顆鑽石的環扣，拍賣之前預估價格640至850萬元台幣，周一拍賣以30萬168美元（約979萬台幣）成交，買主尚未露面，據悉是一名亞洲人士。（國際中心╱綜合外電報導）Producer Tim Burton brings Lewis Carroll's classic novel to the silver screen in the new movie Alice Through the Looking Glass. Burton first brought Carroll's characters to life in Alice in Wonderland. Now, six months after the events of the first movie, Alice must trave l back to Wonderland and through time to save the Mad Hatter. To succeed, however, she must survive the evil Red Queen and a new villain who has been waiting for her return.線上收聽請按audiojs.events.ready(function(){var as = audiojs.cr